FBIS3-33235 "drlat035_r_94006" FBIS-LAT-94-035 Document Type:Daily Report 22 Feb 1994 Peru State of Emergency Extended 60 Days in Piura PA1902163194 Hamburg DPA in Spanish 1611 GMT 19 Feb 94 PA1902163194 Hamburg DPA Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Lima, 19 Feb (DPA) -- Today, the Peruvian Government extended the state of emergency in Huancabamba Province, Piura Department, in northern Peru for 60 days. Therefore, several constitutional guarantees have been suspended and the Armed Forces are responsible for internal order.
